dct_title_s: Plan of the town of Alexandria in the District of Columbia, 1798
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures.; Authorship attributed to George Gilpin in P.L. Phillips' A list of maps of America.; Reprint.; Annotated in pencil in lower margin: Alexandria. An edition of 165 impressions from the original copper-plate. Published 26 June 1944 by Mangum & Josephine Weeks. No. 60.; Oriented with north toward the upper right.; Includes index to points of interest and notes.
